/**
 * SenseCAP Indicator Motion Driver
 *
 * Controls object background colors on an openHASP device (SenseCAP Indicator)
 * via MQTT. Each sensor slot (motion or contact) maps to one openHASP object.
 *
 * openHASP MQTT topic format:
 *   hasp/<nodeName>/command/p<page>b<objectId>.bg_color
 * Payload:
 *   #RRGGBB
 *
 * Sensor semantics (both handled identically at the driver level):
 *   motion  active / contact open / water wet   → colorActive   (default red)
 *   motion inactive / contact closed / water dry / smoke clear → per-type inactive color (after fade)
 *
 * Author: jlslate (slate)
 * Version: 2.6.0  — fix label escape chain to pass icon sequences correctly
 */

